##Video Mah Jongg, cooking a gourmet meal, the stress relief of staying at home in Wuhan | Sandwich Wuhan Daily Book 03

WECHAT china30s

Features, a platform that encourages you to write about your life. Founded in March 2011, it has a sandwich writing school and a media platform, China Sandwich, at the same time, we are committed to apply the story to cross-border product design, urban culture mining, exhibition fairs, space building and other three-dimensional field.

On the eve of the Lunar New Year, I was asked: "should we have a happy new year? " As her family gathered around to watch the gala, she was worried about the epidemic in Wuhan, paying attention to all kinds of news, only to be criticized by her family.

Human Sadness and joy are not mutually exclusive, but they can coexist. Every emotion is real. Panic, anxiety is real, the joy of the holiday that still exists, the happiness of life is real. What we face is not only the opposition of truth and falsehood, but the opposition of one kind of truth to another. These joys and sorrows, for everyone, are not performances, not rhetoric, but the whole of life in the present moment.

On the first day of the siege in Wuhan, Sandwich recruited 50 friends from Wuhan and their hometowns to faithfully document their daily lives at this particular time, and a daily excerpt of their book of the day is published. As a true fragment of the great epidemic, leaving a trace of the common man for the Times.

Today is the third, we choose some Wuhan people at home life slice. Some people video-link in the family group to eat, play Mahjong, some people use this time to stay at home began to frantically tidy up, cleaning, some people in the news often involuntarily cry, decided to stay away from the phone, divert attention..

Everyone is sincerely hoping that everything will be better soon.

01

In the family group,
We video-link to eat, play Mahjong

By Huang Beibei
COORDINATES: Hankou, Wuhan
Occupation: Teacher

The family had booked a big table for more than 20 people to eat together, until January 20, Zhong Nanshan's speech came out, the first time to return the order, their respective Chinese New Year.

Originally, our family was very close to my aunt's family and uncle's family. They were all in a small community. The distance was less than 100 meters in a straight line. We met every weekend. Not only did we have New Year's dinner together every year, we spent almost every day together from the first day of the Lunar New Year to the sixth day of the Lunar New Year, when no other relatives came, they ate and played mah-jongg. This year can only stay at home alone, about six o'clock video-dinner.

At 4:30 pm my dad got up to cook, I said: "You cook a few dishes Ah, so early to prepare" , he thought, said "not a few dishes, is a little early" , and sat down.

At six o'clock, we cooked four dishes: Braised Yellow Croaker, Chinese cabbage, fried beef with Chili, and egg soup with golden mushroom. This is the worst New Year's meal I've ever had.

At six o'clock, to the group opened a video, three finally gathered together a cup, each began to eat, uncle's family has two small grandchildren, the most noisy noisy. My father said quietly: "There are children is more lively. ". I doubt it was meant for me. Our family of four people busy finished playing Mahjong, aunt's three people, their silence to eat vegetables, their silence to see the phone.

In less than half an hour, our family was the first to finish eating, from the table to the Mahjong table. The other two families looked at US enviously and urged us to continue to broadcast the Mahjong pageant live and have a good time.

02

On the first day of the official closure of Wuhan,
I'm seven days away from my due date
Run with the wind, Girl
COORDINATES: Wuhan
Occupation: General Clerk

New Year's Eve, the first day of the official closure of Wuhan, I am still seven days away from the due date.

Yesterday morning, I opened my eyes, I saw the news of the closing of Wuhan on my mobile phone. I felt like an island, under the depressed dome, my mind was full of the idea of "covering the nest, with the whole egg" . My husband knew the news before me, see I woke up immediately the first time hold me tightly, the little guy across the belly a small protest, the husband said his wife don't worry too much, this is we accompany darling through the first difficult! After a day of adjustment, arranged how to nest at home next, how to deal with special circumstances and other matters, the mood slowly relaxed.

When life is in trouble, why not take it as an opportunity to slow down, not hurry back to the full attention of family and dull day, is also a rare experience!

Today, I plan to put all my energy on the traditional reunion dinner, and start playing the old dust, listing the new year's menu, pasting spring couplets, and preparing the reunion dinner. Finally, I, my husband and my mother-in-law enjoy the feast together. Although this year because of pneumonia only three of us in Wuhan, and father-in-law brother-in-law, sister-in-law nephew separated from two places, but really very contented and grateful! Mother-in-law a person put out a table full of ten dishes "perfect" reunion dinner, the mother-in-law drink a little wine also reminded her of the infinite past.

Looking at her red face, and her husband when the smile when sad when the words slowly talk about the past, present and future, I touch the belly is rolling baby, trance feel a wife, a mother for family, it can be soft as HELL OR TOUGH AS HELL!

Baby, although you haven't been born yet, your mother has been beating her heart with you for nearly ten months. I believe you can share all my joys, sorrows and sorrows. Perhaps you can also feel the difference of this Spring Festival, what a different experience for your life. Mother will protect you from completely to let you go gradually, but love you, hope you peace and joy of the original heart will never change.

03

Mom and dad were watching TV,
While playing a set of eight section brocade

By Xiaoman
Coordinates: Xu Dong, Wuhan
Occupation: New Media

In fact, this kind of moment, everyone will inevitably fear, especially a person at home friends, can try to chat with friends, than a person at home to brush the phone more and more panic. And at times like this, don't scare yourself by giving a real example of what happened to me.

Last night, I brushed my teeth. As usual, I pressed the electric toothbrush and began to brush. But when I looked into the sink, "Oh my God! " It was foam mixed with blood. Then I looked in the mirror and saw that there was blood from my gums to my front teeth, i felt like a pill. But a big mouth moment feel lips particularly painful, only to find that the original just lips broken skin. The moment patted a head to oneself toward the mirror to say, "four not four silly" .

In fact, this week, from Monday to now, the closure of cities, motor vehicles ban, the country's 30 provinces and cities launched a first-level response... although these are happening, but the feeling is particularly unreal. Suddenly a lot of information, can only slowly digest, the reality of the worst, but also slowly accept it.

Let's take a look at what we're doing in Wuhan.

The life lies in the movement, not only can alleviate the pressure, but also can exercise the body! My parents watched TV while playing a set of Baduanjin. You can picture two bears moving..

Friends in the group shouting online games.

And, isn't the Spring Festival about playing Mahjong? We're GONNA need one more for the poker game on the phone.

Or, like me, is typing fast at the moment..

The city's closed, but we're still living. So, face it with a light heart!

04

Carefully planned things to do,
Tell yourself it'll pass

By Wang Guima
COORDINATES: Wuchang
Occupation: Children's book editor

Two days in a row in anxiety and self-construction, the more painful news, see behind, what can not do the feeling of powerlessness deeper. Finally decided to give up following the news, take good care of themselves.

Determined to buck up, they carefully planned the New Year's Eve to do things. Clean-up, home disinfection, careful preparation of meals, to the cat bath, write epidemic diary, a person's New Year's Eve, also because of the enrichment has become a bit lively.

The weather outside the window is too much in keeping with the mood

Woke up at 8:30, woke up early. The weather is not very good, cloudy day still under the drizzle, simple preparation of breakfast, carefully selected dishes, the beginning of my own New Year's Eve. It's never too complicated to eat alone, with lots of CARBS, protein, vegetables, and milk, all balanced as much as possible.

Prepare your breakfast carefully

Then open the window ventilation, tidy up the room, clean up, spray diluted 84 disinfection water to the home, trivial housework finished, so the morning passed. I called my family and asked how they were doing, and my mother said, you're a handful. But how did she know that I was only doing it so I wouldn't get emotionally Random Thoughts?

At noon because to do housework, simply do a bowl of fried rice, dinner is after all, can not be too careless. Stewed ribs and turnip soup, and stir-fried bean sprouts, staple food is years ago and mother together at home wrapped in Shepherd's purse pork dumplings. Although no one to push a cup for a cup, the New Year dinner table can not be without wine, a person also poured himself a cup of plum wine, SIP, the bottom of my heart, I wish you all the new year, safe and smooth.

A person's New Year's Eve dinner, but also must have dumplings

On the morning of the first day of the new year, they were bombarded by family members on wechat because of a video of bodies being left unattended in hospitals that went viral on Weibo (a rumor has been refuted) . Relatives Group there are more than a community around the suspected patients were taken away by ambulance news, the family is very nervous, repeatedly told me not to go out. In fact on the 23rd, I was in a number of local groups are crazy about the epidemic. All kinds of gossip, donations, requests for help, little videos of what's going on inside the hospital... all kinds of things, all of which are hard to spot.

Then came the bad news: The high school classmate I hadn't seen for years was a nurse at a large general hospital in Hankou. When I got in touch with her, she told me that her hospital had been requisitioned to be a special hospital for the epidemic, as soon as the hospital facilities are in place. And another good friend has a fever, to the hospital check-up, has not yet come up with results (although there is a probability not virus pneumonia) , in the hospital isolation. We do not know what to say on Wechat, type out the word to delete and type, type and delete. Nothing can be done except to take care of yourself and to take care of yourself. The feeling of powerlessness almost took my breath away and I burst into tears.

It's a traditional Chinese character for "Fu" 
I hope everything goes away soon

At 4 pm on January 25, officials in Wuhan announced that private cars would be banned tomorrow. Once again, the wechat groups fried their pots. A friend who lived in Hankou didn't have a large supermarket nearby and needed to go far away to buy food and supplies. I asked her if there was enough food in her home, it's GonNa get a lot harder. Instead, she was more relaxed than I was and comforted me by telling me that it would be a good exercise to go on a shared bike instead.

At the end of The Host, the girl is killed by a monster, while her father, who should be heartbroken and desperate, acts as if nothing has happened. After the disaster, life is calm again, everything is normal, the pain is hidden under the water. The same is true of us now, fear and anxiety slowly accumulated, and then deep breathing, tell yourself will pass, quietly waiting.

05

Before the city's ban on motor vehicles,
My family's stock-taking

By rain
COORDINATES: Wuchang District, Wuhan
Jiyuqiao Street
Occupation: urban planner

I didn't stock up on New Year's goods because I planned to go on a trip, before "box horse" can grab a single, bought a bit, later "box horse" can not get a single, the supermarket the day before the container was empty, the next day, I have been thinking, AH, from out of stock to panic buying, so when do I go shopping?

Out of stock, we can understand, after all, the government and enterprises to mobilize materials need time, this is China in, stop production in China.

Panic, panic, I get it. We've never been through anything like this.

My calm, you should also be able to understand, my big Chinese Wuhan, will not be short of food and drink.

So on their own and her husband carried out the plan of the supply of vegetables, decided to go to the morning of the first day of shopping, is the least time customers.

Target: Vegetable Market, horse box
Equipment: hat, mask, glasses, disposable gloves
How to get there: by car

Global Village supermarket downstairs, open, there are several stalls offering rich vegetables, Hongshan District Moss 25, common moss 15, cabbage 6, it is normal, as usual, after all, it is the first day, this can not be considered a surge in prices... At this time the guard, are heroes, decisively took out his cell phone, brush his receipt code...

Zhongbai Supermarket, also few customers, bought the shampoo to grandma, also bought some snacks drinks, enrich life.

Box Horse, not a few customers, dishes rich, almost complete, especially rich green leafy vegetables, see me my eyes are green. There is milk, for many days did not get the Yanshi ranch milk, unexpectedly also have goods. Dried bean curd and processed food are all available. A good old-fashioned charade.

My husband looked at me as if looking at aliens, said the security supply, no one with you to rob, you rob... I didn't answer him. I didn't know what to say. I didn't stop.

About six large bags, split in half, sent half to grandma and GRANDPA, and then excitedly went home.

The road passes through the Second Yangtze River Bridge, traffic control, one-lane traffic. No one intercepted it. No one took the temperature.

Wechat received a notice tomorrow at 0:00 the city's vehicle ban management. WECHAT group information such as flood, supermarket lines, goods rush empty...

My husband looked at me like an idiot, and I looked at him like an alien.
"Wife, you are really talented! "

That's right, don't look who's wife...

The confluence of overwhelming information, all point to seriously old friend and base patient, I this old slow branch, allow no accident. Fear, fear, everywhere, cry from time to time, the husband coax not good kind of...

Cry Or don't cry, it's a choice. I CHOOSE TO CRY!

When the People's Liberation Army comes, I cry; when the Doctors Come, I cry; when the Protective Equipment Comes, I cry; when the Medical Classification System is activated, I cry; when the motor vehicle is banned, I cry; when the Community Notice comes, I cry..

Crying is my right, crying is my catharsis, crying is self-relief, but difficult for my husband, he can not feel my fear, can only be helpless to hold me, let people tear freely.

However, this kind of mood, unexpectedly after I go out for a walk, obtained the alleviation. Starting tomorrow, I'M GONNA start working out.

06

Stay at home and tidy up,
Ah Huan Made Fried Meat with carrot and Avocado

By Unger
Coordinates: Wuhan, Hubei
Occupation: Freelancer

My time at home was so slow that I tidied up the kitchen, rearranged the dishes in the disinfected cupboard in a more logical way, and repainted a stainless steel pot that I had burned black a while back.

Free Down will brush the mobile phone, see "from tomorrow on the main city of Wuhan private cars banned on the road, " the news and opinions vary interpretation, all of a sudden and anxiety up. I couldn't digest my impatience, so I channeled it into the only other living thing in the room besides myself -- a Florida woman.

"Toilet Roll only 5 packs, seems not much paper! DETERGENT ONLY HALF A bottle! TOOTHBRUSH IS ALMOST GONE! HOW TO DO! " I yelled at Ah Huan. Ah Huan was completely unaware of my emotions, as if I were offering him a solution to a problem. JD.com home, Tao Xian Da, daily Youxian, Meituan take-out, hungry... we are a needle in a haystack of general brush is still in business.

I was lucky enough to find a sturdy Rawson's on ele.me, and I ordered three bags of Kleenex, toothbrush, two boxes of instant noodles, and two boxes of milk. The shop closed quickly after I placed my order, but luckily I had a rider to pick it up.

The riders will be here soon. I opened the door and my brother, a biker in a blue surgical mask, threw the bag at me from nearly a meter away. I said thank you and quickly closed the door, put the bag on the door of the "disinfection area" began to carefully disinfection. The outside of the bag and each item are wiped down with a 99% sterile paper towel, followed by a towel handle.

Dinner a Huan made: STIR FRY Dutch beans, cucumber scrambled eggs, and carrot and Avocado fried meat, meaning: Dutch beans do not eat will be old, cucumber buy more, avocado do not eat will be bad..



07

Wrapped a gift,
When the Cherry blossoms bloom, give them to friends and relatives

By Sanu
Coordinates: Wuhan, Hubei
Occupation: Teacher

Yesterday a good friend and I chat, I said I feel like a roller coaster, the news will be non-stop crying. After learning that I was lightheaded, with constant chest tightness, and had difficulty falling asleep, she, who was doing psychological counseling, forwarded this to me.

"In case you haven't noticed, constantly scrolling through traumatic messages on your phone is a sign of a state of stress. Individuals without special training, without professional support, don't be exposed in large doses to too harsh a flow of information, and can be drawn into, and replaced by, alternative trauma. Friends, if you have similar dizziness, nausea, heart pain of the physical discomfort, please leave twitter, go to sleep! Or do something else for a while. Protecting our physical and mental health, strengthening our immunity, and not contributing to the chaos of our country are the few things that we ordinary people can do well..."

After reading a lot of text, I realized that I was having an overreaction, so today I consciously turned away from my phone, shifted my focus, selectively read messages, and prevented information overload. Also in my wechat group of Sisters:

Members from now on
1. Only official links and messages are accepted in the group. If not, please take responsibility for your own words.
2. Don't play up the panic, give a red envelope if it's against the rules!
3. Of course jokes are free to be posted."

And then it got really good, and the whole group stopped being so anxious and insecure, and everyone turned their attention to positive energy and good things. For example, the hard nuclear epidemic prevention measures in Henan Province, such as drying at home to do baking, doing manual, DIY drink milk tea, and so on. We seem to have suddenly stolen a lot of time to enjoy a real vacation, to try to be alone with ourselves, and to develop close relationships with our families. I wrapped a gift in the morning, want to wait for the Cherry blossom, can go out when, send to the family and friends after the robbery.

When doing handwork, my baby accompany me beside, although will also make trouble, but also can be controlled, not to "Husky" degree. I remember the last time I took her to see the cherry blossoms. She yawned under the tree and I caught her doing it. It was only 10 months later. I hope that when the Cherry blossoms bloom this year, we can smooth out the crisis of the epidemic and take her to see it, then in the tree inadvertently smell the spring, lazy to Yawn.

On the morning of the first day of the new year, they were bombarded by family members on wechat because of a video of bodies being left unattended in hospitals that went viral on Weibo (a rumor has been refuted) . Relatives Group there are more than a community around the suspected patients were taken away by ambulance news, the family is very nervous, repeatedly told me not to go out. In fact on the 23rd, I was in a number of local groups are crazy about the epidemic. All kinds of gossip, donations, requests for help, little videos of what's going on inside the hospital... all kinds of things, all of which are hard to spot.

Then came the bad news: The high school classmate I hadn't seen for years was a nurse at a large general hospital in Hankou. When I got in touch with her, she told me that her hospital had been requisitioned to be a special hospital for the epidemic, as soon as the hospital facilities are in place. And another good friend has a fever, to the hospital check-up, has not yet come up with results (although there is a probability not virus pneumonia) , in the hospital isolation. We do not know what to say on Wechat, type out the word to delete and type, type and delete. Nothing can be done except to take care of yourself and to take care of yourself. The feeling of powerlessness almost took my breath away and I burst into tears.

At 4 pm on January 25, officials in Wuhan announced that private cars would be banned tomorrow. Once again, the wechat groups fried their pots. A friend who lived in Hankou didn't have a large supermarket nearby and needed to go far away to buy food and supplies. I asked her if there was enough food in her home, it's GonNa get a lot harder. Instead, she was more relaxed than I was and comforted me by telling me that it would be a good exercise to go on a shared bike instead.

At the end of The Host, the girl is killed by a monster, while her father, who should be heartbroken and desperate, acts as if nothing has happened. After the disaster, life is calm again, everything is normal, the pain is hidden under the water. The same is true of us now, fear and anxiety slowly accumulated, and then deep breathing, tell yourself will pass, quietly waiting.

I didn't stock up on New Year's goods because I planned to go on a trip, before "box horse" can grab a single, bought a bit, later "box horse" can not get a single, the supermarket the day before the container was empty, the next day, I have been thinking, AH, from out of stock to panic buying, so when do I go shopping?

Out of stock, we can understand, after all, the government and enterprises to mobilize materials need time, this is China in, stop production in China.

Panic, panic, I get it. We've never been through anything like this.

My calm, you should also be able to understand, my big Chinese Wuhan, will not be short of food and drink.

So on their own and her husband carried out the plan of the supply of vegetables, decided to go to the morning of the first day of shopping, is the least time customers.

Target: Vegetable Market, horse box
Equipment: hat, mask, glasses, disposable gloves
How to get there: by car

Global Village supermarket downstairs, open, there are several stalls offering rich vegetables, Hongshan District Moss 25, common moss 15, cabbage 6, it is normal, as usual, after all, it is the first day, this can not be considered a surge in prices... At this time the guard, are heroes, decisively took out his cell phone, brush his receipt code...

Zhongbai Supermarket, also few customers, bought the shampoo to grandma, also bought some snacks drinks, enrich life.

Box Horse, not a few customers, dishes rich, almost complete, especially rich green leafy vegetables, see me my eyes are green. There is milk, for many days did not get the Yanshi ranch milk, unexpectedly also have goods. Dried bean curd and processed food are all available. A good old-fashioned charade.

My husband looked at me as if looking at aliens, said the security supply, no one with you to rob, you rob... I didn't answer him. I didn't know what to say. I didn't stop.

About six large bags, split in half, sent half to grandma and GRANDPA, and then excitedly went home.

The road passes through the Second Yangtze River Bridge, traffic control, one-lane traffic. No one intercepted it. No one took the temperature.

Wechat received a notice tomorrow at 0:00 the city's vehicle ban management. WECHAT group information such as flood, supermarket lines, goods rush empty...

My husband looked at me like an idiot, and I looked at him like an alien.
"Wife, you are really talented! "

That's right, don't look who's wife...

The confluence of overwhelming information, all point to seriously old friend and base patient, I this old slow branch, allow no accident. Fear, fear, everywhere, cry from time to time, the husband coax not good kind of...

Cry Or don't cry, it's a choice. I CHOOSE TO CRY!

When the People's Liberation Army comes, I cry; when the Doctors Come, I cry; when the Protective Equipment Comes, I cry; when the Medical Classification System is activated, I cry; when the motor vehicle is banned, I cry; when the Community Notice comes, I cry..

Crying is my right, crying is my catharsis, crying is self-relief, but difficult for my husband, he can not feel my fear, can only be helpless to hold me, let people tear freely.

However, this kind of mood, unexpectedly after I go out for a walk, obtained the alleviation. Starting tomorrow, I'M GONNA start working out.

Free Down will brush the mobile phone, see "from tomorrow on the main city of Wuhan private cars banned on the road, " the news and opinions vary interpretation, all of a sudden and anxiety up. I couldn't digest my impatience, so I channeled it into the only other living thing in the room besides myself -- a Florida woman.

"Toilet Roll only 5 packs, seems not much paper! DETERGENT ONLY HALF A bottle! TOOTHBRUSH IS ALMOST GONE! HOW TO DO! " I yelled at Ah Huan. Ah Huan was completely unaware of my emotions, as if I were offering him a solution to a problem. JD.com home, Tao Xian Da, daily Youxian, Meituan take-out, hungry... we are a needle in a haystack of general brush is still in business.

I was lucky enough to find a sturdy Rawson's on ele.me, and I ordered three bags of Kleenex, toothbrush, two boxes of instant noodles, and two boxes of milk. The shop closed quickly after I placed my order, but luckily I had a rider to pick it up.

The riders will be here soon. I opened the door and my brother, a biker in a blue surgical mask, threw the bag at me from nearly a meter away. I said thank you and quickly closed the door, put the bag on the door of the "disinfection area" began to carefully disinfection. The outside of the bag and each item are wiped down with a 99% sterile paper towel, followed by a towel handle.

Dinner a Huan made: STIR FRY Dutch beans, cucumber scrambled eggs, and carrot and Avocado fried meat, meaning: Dutch beans do not eat will be old, cucumber buy more, avocado do not eat will be bad..

Yesterday a good friend and I chat, I said I feel like a roller coaster, the news will be non-stop crying. After learning that I was lightheaded, with constant chest tightness, and had difficulty falling asleep, she, who was doing psychological counseling, forwarded this to me.

"In case you haven't noticed, constantly scrolling through traumatic messages on your phone is a sign of a state of stress. Individuals without special training, without professional support, don't be exposed in large doses to too harsh a flow of information, and can be drawn into, and replaced by, alternative trauma. Friends, if you have similar dizziness, nausea, heart pain of the physical discomfort, please leave twitter, go to sleep! Or do something else for a while. Protecting our physical and mental health, strengthening our immunity, and not contributing to the chaos of our country are the few things that we ordinary people can do well..."

After reading a lot of text, I realized that I was having an overreaction, so today I consciously turned away from my phone, shifted my focus, selectively read messages, and prevented information overload. Also in my wechat group of Sisters:

Members from now on
1. Only official links and messages are accepted in the group. If not, please take responsibility for your own words.
2. Don't play up the panic, give a red envelope if it's against the rules!
3. Of course jokes are free to be posted."

And then it got really good, and the whole group stopped being so anxious and insecure, and everyone turned their attention to positive energy and good things. For example, the hard nuclear epidemic prevention measures in Henan Province, such as drying at home to do baking, doing manual, DIY drink milk tea, and so on. We seem to have suddenly stolen a lot of time to enjoy a real vacation, to try to be alone with ourselves, and to develop close relationships with our families. I wrapped a gift in the morning, want to wait for the Cherry blossom, can go out when, send to the family and friends after the robbery.
